Shoutout to Trickster for finding this and showing it to me.

Before the patch, you were able to flick off of a surf and skip to the next booster. This was incredibly hard and anti-fun during a run, so I decided to patch it out.

_sText:
made this map out of frustration from somewhat failing to make a different, higher quality map. I wanted to make something with an easy theme, so I decided to work on this. It's just an average map made for fun.Â 

The map itself is T3 and probably around 1:15:1:30. I haven't had any testers though so I could be off from that.

There are three bonuses
1st bonus: 10-20 seconds & slightly technical/climby
2nd bonus: 15-25 seconds & strafey
3rd bonus: 25-35 seconds & strafey but with some small climbs, surfs and boosters
If your server doesn't support multiple bonuses, I'd suggest the 1st bonus.
The map hasn't been tested by other people so if there are some dumb skips, lmk
